Module com.psymk6
Package com.psymk6.abstracts

Class CanvasObjectModel

java.lang.Object
com.psymk6.abstracts.CanvasObjectModel
Direct Known Subclasses:
BlockadeModel, LiveCanvasObjectModel, ScoreModel
public abstract class CanvasObjectModel extends Object
This abstract class represents a basic model for objects on a canvas, providing properties such as coordinates, width, and height.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Mateusz Klocek
